Authentication:
1. JWT Implementation (Access & Refresh Tokens)
2. HttpOnly Cookie Storage (Secure & SameSite: None Flags)
3. Password Hashing (Slow Hashing with Argon2 or bcrypt)
4. Refresh Token Rotation
5. Hashed Refresh Token Storage (MongoDB)
6. Breach Detection Logic (Token Family Revocation)
7. Redis Blacklisting (Access Token Revocation)
8. Token Versioning (Logout From All Devices)
9. CSRF Protection (Double Submit Cookie/Custom Header)
10. Device Fingerprinting (Tracking IP & User-Agent)


2FA Authentication:
1. TOTP Support (Google Authenticator/Authy)
2. Email/SMS OTP (Nodemailer & Redis TTL)
3. Secret Key Generation & QR Code
4. Backup/Recovery Codes
5. 2FA Setup & Disabling Logic


Social Login: 
1. OAuth 2.0 Protocol
2. OpenID Connect (OIDC)
3. Google Strategy Implementation
4. Profile Mapping & Account Linking (Social to Local DB)


Dashboard:
1. Active Session Manager (View & Revoke Specific Devices)
2. Security Audit Logs (Failed Login/Activity Tracking)
3. Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) (Admin/Editor/User Permissions)
4. "Secret Vault" CRUD (Data protected by Authorization)
5. Password Reset System (Email Link & Crypto-Token)
6. Account Verification Flow (Email Link)